Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次上到74页，现在接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的生活和以前没什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为人处世的高手有一个共同的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事留有余地，不仅自己能过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚念到的地方，大家重念一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我调到这里也要拿出点成绩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让他们成绩变好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能出绝招了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手机收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上课有这么无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家乖乖好好上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会给你们福利的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此为原则决定处世思路的取舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在吵什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先脱内裤    你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到皮肤的害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有阴部全部露     还有阴毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有做到脱光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会更害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算手遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手打开全部让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超想穿衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是处女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但第一次这样看肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒都硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想出喇叭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还装什么清高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉肉棒又打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就开始出喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真低级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被神遗忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒顶到股间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有震动感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好低级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:07:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的插入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开始抽动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒粗乱的乱插
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好低级的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要长大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就插得更深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师    也动的更快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不停扭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞阿    看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可露多点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面不停地插
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎没了      我要看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都可以专心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啊     好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要平均50分才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿内裤就静不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚一时运动脱了  实在不应该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:16:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但内裤湿的再穿上     好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下去买免洗内裤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，资料给你，要放在哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便放着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我看看里面的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空的话帮我放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空着的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮我     知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干嘛？    不是帮你放吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是放这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是诱惑我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没穿内裤？    而且都湿了。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也很想要     不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是欲求不满啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你满足的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热      哪边热？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我前面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.08,0:23:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.28,0:24:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.40,0:24:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这边
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.00,0:25:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞     看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.36,0:25:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.52,0:26:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想插       不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.56,0:26:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.92,0:27:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.56,0:27:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我爽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.32,0:29:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要让我爽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.44,0:30:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.20,0:30:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.16,0:30:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好低级
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.36,0:31:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.28,0:31:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换这边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.88,0:33:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.48,0:34:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不停干
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.56,0:34:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.15,0:34:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.40,0:34:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再干吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不停干
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.96,0:36:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.28,0:36:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才刚射
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.96,0:37:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.00,0:37:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.84,0:39:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超猛的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.24,0:39:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.36,0:40:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.84,0:40:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师      怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.32,0:40:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有么有受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.32,0:40:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.12,0:40:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摸哪边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧    不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.00,0:41:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.64,0:41:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子有撞到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.40,0:41:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.56,0:41:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在摸哪边啊      好像很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变红了    最好要冰
