Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.16,1:22:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师      你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.88,1:23:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对她做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.40,1:23:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上课啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.16,1:23:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么课啊      没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.04,1:23:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.92,1:23:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打扰我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.24,1:23:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.72,1:23:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.56,1:23:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们的分数是真的    有提高
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.32,1:23:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过程不重要     重要是结果
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.52,1:24:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.40,1:24:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.24,1:24:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天大岛老师要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.72,1:24:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天让你们看看    我们做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.68,1:24:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们要一边打手枪
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.68,1:24:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.00,1:24:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.00,1:24:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好突然
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.56,1:24:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在学生面前？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.56,1:24:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要帮我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.04,1:25:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大岛老师摸我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.20,1:25:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.60,1:25:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要看好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.88,1:26:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.44,1:26:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在看了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.84,1:26:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部要看
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.68,1:26:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.44,1:27:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴蒂好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.20,1:27:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔它会舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.28,1:27:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很赞
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.64,1:28:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何      好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.68,1:28:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.96,1:28:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说喜欢屁眼？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.00,1:29:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.80,1:30:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.00,1:30:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打手枪
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.92,1:31:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.08,1:32:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.68,1:32:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家先要吗？        想
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.32,1:32:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.76,1:32:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.68,1:32:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软
