Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.80,1:33:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.32,1:34:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我     兴奋起来
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.40,1:34:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.60,1:35:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.36,1:35:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到你这样     我就硬挺
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.20,1:35:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家我可以被她吹喇叭吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.32,1:35:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.80,1:35:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先用了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.92,1:35:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没插吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.08,1:35:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看着
